{"tid":645532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【抄襲醜聞】強國教授獲設計界奧斯卡獎 被爆翻dup英畫師作品","createTime":"2018-04-28T08:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T10:00:30.000Z","uid":48083,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"dd612810178e0fe90af9e2178548903951913340","tid":645532,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T08:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/161922_1bbc3d906a3d5ebbbd9a20b09dce3610.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F161922_1bbc3d906a3d5ebbbd9a20b09dce3610.png&h=1df2fab5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/161928_5a5df5eaa36e8e6e2ef43ff369ad31c7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F161928_5a5df5eaa36e8e6e2ef43ff369ad31c7.png&h=1959aace&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/161933_567d2110f95e0214607491a0325ae2ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F161933_567d2110f95e0214607491a0325ae2ad.png&h=4a195f23&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/28/161946_b02c6c9926427f12a6dc2ff2d3f7277d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F28%2F161946_b02c6c9926427f12a6dc2ff2d3f7277d.png&h=3e109700&s={SIZE}\" />西安美術學院爆出教授獲獎作品抄襲醜聞！該校新晉副教授樊雨的兩項作品，去年10月榮獲德國紅點獎最高榮譽獎至尊獎及紅點獎，卻被指涉嫌抄襲英國插畫師Russell Cobb的作品。主辦紅點獎的德國機構已撤銷頒給樊雨的獎項，西安美術學院更決定，暫停樊雨的副教授任職資格。<br />\n<br />\n本月24日，微信公眾號「抄襲的藝術」發佈文章，稱西安美術學院一位樊姓青年教師的作品《Open Air Cinema National Museum》於去年10月27日榮獲德國紅點獎最高榮譽獎至尊獎（Red Dot: Best of the Best），其另一部作品《 Brain Art Museum》則榮獲紅點獎。（德國紅點獎創立於1955年，被喻為設計界的「奧斯卡獎」。）<br />\n<br />\n文章指，該名樊姓青年作品，涉嫌抄襲英國插畫師Russell Cobb在2011年的作品《New IdeasII》和《Note talking》，並給出了作品比圖。從中可以看到，樊姓教師的作品中很多元素，均和該插畫師的作品相差無幾，只是在部份區域暈染了一些色彩。有指，該名教師正是西安美術學院副教授樊雨。<br />\n<br />\n德國紅點傳播和公共關係主管Steinhoff證實，早前頒發給樊雨的Red Dot: Best of the Best獎項已被撤銷。而樊雨已經從名人堂和線上展覽中移走，不再擁有紅點獲獎者的身份或在紅點獎中保有的任何位置。<br />\n<br />\nSteinhoff稱，採取這一行動是因為他們確定樊雨使用了Russell Cobb的插圖，但他在參賽時並沒有提出Russell Cobb為插畫家和版權所有人。樊雨在提交獎項時指，西安音樂廳是其客戶，但紅點主辦方並沒有看到這方面的證據，因此紅點認為這部參賽作品是假的，侵犯了Russell Cobb的知識產權。Steinhoff說：「我們將保留以故意欺詐對樊雨采取法律行動的權利。他不但損害了原創者的聲譽，也損害了西安音樂廳和紅點設計獎的良好聲譽。」<br />\n<br />\n據悉，西安美術學院早前發出公報，稱學院召開黨委擴大會議，決定暫停樊雨的副教授任職資格，並就事件組成聯合調查組進行深入調查。<br />\n<br />\n紅星新聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180428/58128352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180428%2F58128352&d=w%2FpB5ZNj24SnWsdMZ3SEwjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=14784a46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180428%2F58128352&h=fadc4407\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180428/58128352</a>"},{"pid":"8c4383e16a8a5ecdceac4e71a9470ed636b2f102","tid":645532,"uid":40763,"like":4,"dislike":23,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T08:22:11.000Z","msg":"邊撚到似<br />\n仆街德國佬欺人太甚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b1629d5629a7141ff63328082036af3d5bb23e","tid":645532,"uid":50457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T08:22:13.000Z","msg":"要不是<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國或"},{"pid":"3bd0ebbb78648902ab876f5370589cc72d0f6cb6","tid":645532,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T08:24:12.000Z","msg":"係咪低能"},{"pid":"b831c446021980dd9a38a29a43ac11385e3ffb8c","tid":645532,"uid":12000,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"cit